data.description: Here is the deal you have been looking for! With little money and sweat equity, this home will be worth over 200k! This 3 bedroom, 1 full bath and 1 half bath property only needs some cosmetic TLC but is a great deal! This end unit offers a yard 3 times the size of most in the neighborhood, great layout, a wood stove to offset your heating bill, updated HVAC, addition on the rear of home that walks out to a deck and more! Hurry to see this one, it will not last long!
